    "content": "<table style=\"height: 85px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 118px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3><strong>Name</strong></h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 478px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3><strong>Crit Effect</strong></h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 92px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3><strong>Type</strong></h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 118px; text-align: center;\">Hand it Over</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 478px; text-align: center;\">Unless you succeed at a Reflex saving throw, your target gains possessions of your weapon.</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 92px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3>Melee</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 118px; text-align: center;\">Broken</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 478px; text-align: center;\">Your weapon's current Hit Points are reduced to its Broken Threshold. If already broken, the weapon takes 3d6 damage, ignoring Hardness.</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 92px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3>Ranged</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 118px; text-align: center;\">Smash the Floor</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 478px; text-align: center;\">You kick up a cloud of dust, becoming blinded until the end of your next turn.</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 92px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3>Unarmed</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 118px; text-align: center;\">You made 'em Faster</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 478px; text-align: center;\">The target is quickened for 2 rounds.</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px; width: 92px; text-align: center;\">\n<h3>Spell</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"> </h3>",
